 SPIRV/CMakeLists.txt                       | 14 ++++----------
 StandAlone/CMakeLists.txt                  | 11 ++++-------
 glslang/OSDependent/Unix/CMakeLists.txt    |  7 +++----
 glslang/OSDependent/Windows/CMakeLists.txt |  3 +--
 hlsl/CMakeLists.txt                        |  5 ++---
 6 files changed, 15 insertions(+), 28 deletions(-)

